Class SessionFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment
      • org.shingo.shingoapp.ui.events.SessionFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, OnTaskCompleteListener

    public class SessionFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
implements OnTaskCompleteListener
    A fragment representing a list of SSessions.

    Activities containing this fragment MUST implement the SessionFragment.OnListFragmentInteractionListener interface.
